            <div type="transcript" id="F1130A">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>The Frost of Death was on the Pane </l>
                    <l>Protect your flower said He </l>
                    <l>Like sailors fighting with a leak </l>
                    <l>We fought Mortality - </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Our passive flower we held to Sea</l>
                    <l>To mountain to the Sun </l>
                    <l>But even on his scarlet shelf </l>
                    <l>To crawl the Frost <app type="emendation"><lem>began</lem><rdg>begun</rdg></app>
 </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>We pried him back </l>
                    <l>Ourselves we wedged</l>
                    <l>Himself and Her between </l>
                    <l>But easy as a narrow snake </l>
                    <l>He forked his way along - </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Till all her helpless beauty bent </l>
                    <l>And then our wrath <app type="emendation"><lem>began</lem><rdg>begun</rdg></app>
</l>
                    <l>We hunted him to his Ravine<app type="division"><lem><pb/></lem></app>
 </l>
                    <l>We chased Him to his Den </l>
                    <l>We hated Life and hated Death </l>
                    <l>And nowhere was to go </l>
                    <l>Than Sea and Continent there is</l>
                    <l>A larger - it is Woe - </l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
